            <div style="display: inline !important; text-align: left;"><span style="color: #2c26f9; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-weight: 800;">RESEARCH COLLABORATION FORM For possible collaboration with</span><b style="font-weight: normal;"> the Pacific Neuropsychiatric Institute &nbsp;in research or on research projects or data analysis please complete the following. &nbsp;There are an enormous number of potential papers available to&nbsp;</b></span><span style="color: #2c26f9; font-weight: bold; font-size: x-small;"><i>independent</i></span><font color="#2c26f9" size="1"><b>&nbsp;research fellows and other master's level or doctoral candidates. </b></font><br />
