            <span style="color: #2c26f9; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-small;">
            &nbsp;Once you've completed this form you may be required to send electronically a curriculum vitae, references, a letter written by you motivating what you want to collaborate in, forms that you may be sent including non-disclosure agreements, and any other information you deem pertinent. Note these are not paid positions. Dr Neppe estimates there are tens of papers that can easily be produced per year this way. We cannot guarantee responding but you may also want to email the Pacific Neuropsychiatric Institute (in addition to this form) at research@pni.org and attach a curriculum vitae or amplifying letter.&nbsp; <br />
